data.title: 1967) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: John A. JacK Schumann, 47, had been hospitalized about 2 weeks when he was taken by ambulance and died  en route to an Omaha hospital. He was born Jan. 20, 1920 to Mr. and Mrs. John J Schumann Jr., at Montclair, New Jersey. He was a veteran of World War II and served in the Air Force.  He was survived by his wife...
